      "description": "This tour follows along with the [12th unit in the Tune Squad Coaches App Microsoft Learn module](https://docs.microsoft.com/learn/modules/optimize-basketball-player-rest-breaks/12-update-stats).\r\n\r\nThe goal of this function is to handle the game ending. This tour will not be as details as previous tours to give you an opportunity to test your JavaScript.\r\n\r\nClick `next` to get started."
    },
    {
      "file": "main.js",
