      "description": "Just like with the quarter ending, make sure the coach can't move players by setting the `quarterInPlay` variable to true."
    },
    {
      "file": "main.js",
      "line": 267,
      "description": "The average PER for the game should just be the total average PER divided by the total number of quarters. \r\n\r\n**REMEMBER:** By the time this function is called you have not yet captured the average PER for the final quarter. Also, you have a `numQuarters` constant that you created earlier."
